Sarkozy Gains Six Points in Popularity in July to 36%, Ifop Poll Shows

-- B y   A l a n   K a t z
-- 
2011-07-24T08:19:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-24/sarkozy-gains-six-points-in-popularity-in-july-to-36-ifop-poll-shows.html
French President  Nicolas Sarkozy ’s
approval rating jumped six points in July, with 36 percent of
the people surveyed saying they were satisfied with him, a poll
showed.  The president’s popularity rose among senior citizens and
shop owners, according to the survey conducted by polling
company Ifop for weekly Journal du Dimanche. The poll was
conducted by phone on July 21 and July 22, with 960 people aged
18 or over participating. No margin of error was provided.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Alan Katz  in Paris at   akatz5@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Melissa Pozsgay at   mpozsgay@bloomberg.net . 